Name: oidc-agent
Version: 3.3.1
Release: 1.1%{?dist}
Summary: Commandline tool for obtaining OpenID Connect access tokens on the commandline
Group: Misc
License: MIT-License
URL: https://github.com/indigo-dc/oidc-agent
